 Znači, meni je za onih 400 kuna godinu danas,

157
00:14:27,760 --> 00:14:31,180
 kojim smo mi morali živjeti u Zagrebu,

158
00:14:32,060 --> 00:14:34,440
 meni je ovo sad top, razumiješ mi?

159
00:14:34,440 --> 00:14:36,840
 Sad, da li to nekome puno, malo, ja to ne znam,

160
00:14:36,840 --> 00:14:37,600
 meni je dovoljno.

161
00:14:37,600 --> 00:14:40,940
 Tako da ti kažem, upornost se stiče time,

162
00:14:40,940 --> 00:14:42,520
 kao i sloboda.

163
00:14:42,520 --> 00:14:45,720
 Najlakše je reći, čovjeko, ja sam slobodan,

164
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:47,220
 pa slobodan si koliko imaš para,

165
00:14:47,220 --> 00:14:48,320
 fred, razumiješ mi?

166
00:14:48,320 --> 00:14:50,920
 Kad nisi, kad nemaš para, nisi ni slobodan.

167
00:14:50,920 --> 00:14:52,220
 E, tako je ta upornost.

168
00:14:52,740 --> 00:14:54,700
 Mene je nešto tjeralo da ja uspijem.

169
00:14:54,700 --> 00:14:57,080
 Ja kad sam vidio da ja neću moći zdržati

170
00:14:57,080 --> 00:14:59,900
 sa policijskom plaćom mjesec,

171
00:14:59,900 --> 00:15:02,280
 jer ja to ne mogu, jer ja nisam iz Zagreba,

172
00:15:02,280 --> 00:15:04,440
 ja nemam tu nikoga, ja ne mogu otići preko

173
00:15:04,440 --> 00:15:07,700
 i mama daj mi pet kila piletine,

174
00:15:07,700 --> 00:15:10,360
 mama daj mi praška za pecivo, daj mi ovo.

175
00:15:10,360 --> 00:15:13,180
 Ne, ja nemam nikog, fred, ja moram kupiti stan.

176
00:15:13,180 --> 00:15:14,300
 Oček da ja kupim stan.

177
00:15:14,300 --> 00:15:17,740
 Moro si dići kredit, taj kredit je oduzima pola plaće.

178
00:15:17,740 --> 00:15:19,620
 Da, fred, ali kak da dođem do samobora?

179
00:15:20,200 --> 00:15:22,780
 Ja moram do samobora da ću kredit da kupim auto.

180
00:15:22,780 --> 00:15:25,500
 Da, fred, ja sad nemam, imam jednu trećinu,

181
00:15:25,500 --> 00:15:26,380
 plaćem i ostalo.

182
00:15:26,380 --> 00:15:28,940
 Šta ću sada, fred, moram nekako izmisliti.

183
00:15:28,940 --> 00:15:32,000
 Pa onda kreneš ono, standardno švercanje proteina

184
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:35,000
 iz Slovenije, znaš, pa prodavanje za veću cijenu.

185
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:37,920
 Pa onda se kreneš, bori, cuatiš da ubiti gle,

186
00:15:37,920 --> 00:15:41,160
 pa nije to samo policija jedini faktor

187
00:15:41,160 --> 00:15:42,700
 u tvojom životu koji može određivati

188
00:15:42,700 --> 00:15:44,620
 da ćeš ti biti gladan ili ćeš biti sit.

189
00:15:44,620 --> 00:15:47,900
 E, upravo tu sam ja tu uporno stekao

190
00:15:47,900 --> 00:15:49,560
 kad sam vidio da sam ja gladan, fred,

191
00:15:49,640 --> 00:15:52,140
 da ja nemam šta za jeste vrlo,

192
00:15:52,140 --> 00:15:54,300
 pa ne mogu ja sa sam stokuna preživiti mjesec.

193
00:15:54,300 --> 00:15:56,080
 A šta ne znam, zašto neki ljudi kad se nađu

194
00:15:56,080 --> 00:15:58,340
 u tako teškoj situaciji, neki odustanu i propadnu

195
00:15:58,340 --> 00:16:01,580
 totalno, neki kažu, ovo je zadnja linija obrane,

196
00:16:01,580 --> 00:16:02,280
 ja se moram bojati.

197
00:16:02,280 --> 00:16:04,540
 Ali kak ćeš odustat, frende, pa ne možeš,

198
00:16:04,540 --> 00:16:06,220
 mislim, ja ću ti reći ovako.

199
00:16:06,220 --> 00:16:07,820
 Ima ljudi koji se jednostavno prepusti.

200
00:16:07,820 --> 00:16:10,060
 Ma ti će odustat, pa stara mi je kraljica,

201
00:16:10,060 --> 00:16:11,600
 frende, ti to tražeš upoznat,

202
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:13,320
 ja bih volio nju na jednom podcastu

203
00:16:13,320 --> 00:16:16,280
 posla da ti vidiš koji je to u biti mozak,

204
00:16:16,280 --> 00:16:17,440
 koji je kako to razmišlja.

205
00:16:17,440 --> 00:16:18,960
 Pa ja nisam mogo odustat zbog nje.

206
00:16:18,960 --> 00:16:20,680
 Čak ne zbog starog.

207
00:16:20,680 --> 00:16:21,960
 Pa već se sam malo primakljeno,

208
00:16:21,960 --> 00:16:23,120
 nis možda predaleko.

209
00:16:24,320 --> 00:16:26,820
 A kad se dira koko nje.

210
00:16:26,820 --> 00:16:31,240
 Stara mi je tu, stara mi je tu kraljica,

211
00:16:31,240 --> 00:16:32,720
 znaš, ono, stvarno ti kažem,

212
00:16:32,720 --> 00:16:35,060
 znaš, kad su se najteže stvari

213
00:16:35,060 --> 00:16:36,400
 meni dešavale u životu,

214
00:16:36,400 --> 00:16:39,260
 ja sam ti našao i to često napominjem

215
00:16:39,260 --> 00:16:41,100
 i evo, baš sam rekao možda u ovom podcastu,

216
00:16:41,100 --> 00:16:41,960
 neću puno pričati,

217
00:16:41,960 --> 00:16:43,260
 ali moram se dotaknuti vjere.

218
00:16:43,260 --> 00:16:45,400
 Vjera je nešto što mene pokreće,

219
00:16:45,400 --> 00:16:47,260
 ja ti se ne bojim apsolutno ničega.

220
00:16:47,260 --> 00:16:48,700
 Meni ti je jedan dan čevk napisao,

221
00:16:48,700 --> 00:16:50,020
 da li se ti trebaš bojati Boga?

222
00:16:50,020 --> 00:16:51,220
 Zašto ga se bojim?

223
00:16:52,020 --> 00:16:53,280
 Zašto se ja trebam bojati Boga?

224
00:16:53,280 --> 00:16:53,880
 Zbog čega?

225
00:16:53,880 --> 00:16:55,140
 To on stalno mi neko,

226
00:16:55,140 --> 00:16:57,460
 da li to ti piše u svetom pismu,

227
00:16:57,460 --> 00:16:58,600
 pa nek piše šta hoće,

228
00:16:58,600 --> 00:16:59,540
 zašto bi ga se ja bojati?

229
00:16:59,540 --> 00:17:02,680
 Ja nemam razlog jedan zašto bi se ja bojio Boga.

230
00:17:02,680 --> 00:17:05,320
 Ako poštivaš te zapovjedi koje imaš,

231
00:17:05,320 --> 00:17:07,220
 ako vodiš brigu o tom,

232
00:17:07,220 --> 00:17:09,200
 pa kod mene ne postoji nedjelja

233
00:17:09,200 --> 00:17:12,180
 da sam ja izosto sa sve te mise,

234
00:17:12,180 --> 00:17:12,720
 razumiješ?

235
00:17:12,720 --> 00:17:14,320
 Mora, evo sad prošla je bila u Indiji,

236
00:17:14,320 --> 00:17:16,020
 di da odemo Indiju na misu,

237
00:17:16,020 --> 00:17:16,540
 razumiješ?

238
00:17:16,540 --> 00:17:17,960
 Ne mogu otići u Indiji na misu,

239
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:19,480
 ali nema katoličke crkve.

240
00:17:19,480 --> 00:17:21,180
 Ali opet s druge strane,

241
00:17:21,180 --> 00:17:24,000
 imaš majku koja te strašno motivira,

242
00:17:24,000 --> 00:17:25,220
 koja je kada je najveće zlo,

243
00:17:25,220 --> 00:17:26,140
 kaže daj, ajde,

244
00:17:26,140 --> 00:17:28,060
 već sam ti rekla da u svakom zlo

245
00:17:28,060 --> 00:17:29,380
 nađeš nešto dobro

246
00:17:29,380 --> 00:17:30,160
 i vidiš da je dobro.

247
00:17:30,160 --> 00:17:32,280
 Meni, ja se sad vrtim,

248
00:17:32,280 --> 00:17:33,440
 evo sad kad pričam s tom,

249
00:17:33,440 --> 00:17:35,160
 vrtim situaciju zadnju,

250
00:17:35,160 --> 00:17:36,640
 koja se nama teška kao bite

251
00:17:36,640 --> 00:17:37,080
 i desila,

252
00:17:37,080 --> 00:17:38,340
 ta moja bolnica

253
00:17:38,340 --> 00:17:40,100
 i skoro odsjecanje noge.

254
00:17:40,100 --> 00:17:41,580
 Neka nose nogu,

255
00:17:41,580 --> 00:17:42,360
 vi će mi mati.

256
00:17:42,360 --> 00:17:43,580
 Šta će ti noga brz?

257
00:17:43,580 --> 00:17:44,780
 Pa tvoj didan imao nogu,

258
00:17:44,780 --> 00:17:45,740
 pa bio dobar čovjek.

259
00:17:45,740 --> 00:17:46,880
 Kažeš uti,

260
00:17:46,880 --> 00:17:47,880
 dobro nije karcinom.

261
00:17:47,880 --> 00:17:48,560
 I smije se.

262
00:17:48,560 --> 00:17:49,960
 I ti plaćeš ono,

263
00:17:49,960 --> 00:17:51,700
 ja mislim si kakva ova žena budala,

264
00:17:51,700 --> 00:17:52,540
 majku ti.

265
00:17:52,540 --> 00:17:53,540
 Pa di ćeš to reći.

266
00:17:53,540 --> 00:17:54,960
 Ali u biti je tako.

267
00:17:54,960 --> 00:17:56,400
 Tako je, vrate.

268
00:17:56,400 --> 00:17:57,380
 Stvarno je tako.

269
00:17:57,380 --> 00:17:58,680
 Šta će ti noga?

270
00:17:58,680 --> 00:18:00,060
 Ako ne valja,

271
00:18:00,060 --> 00:18:00,660
 pa nosi.

272
00:18:00,660 --> 00:18:01,700
 Pa tako i sa zubom.

273
00:18:01,700 --> 00:18:03,200
 Ti ćeš popravljati zub

274
00:18:03,200 --> 00:18:04,120
 tisuću puta.

275
00:18:08,340 --> 00:18:09,820
 Jednom kad se nešto pokvari,

276
00:18:09,820 --> 00:18:11,400
 stvarno je teško popraviti.

277
00:18:11,400 --> 00:18:13,680
 Jer ja imam tih ozljeda na sebi,

278
00:18:13,680 --> 00:18:15,260
 što je 14. operacija.

279
00:18:15,260 --> 00:18:16,460
 Ja to znam.

280
00:18:16,460 --> 00:18:18,100
 Stvarno je teško vratiti

281
00:18:18,100 --> 00:18:19,340
 u prvo bitno stanje.

282
00:18:19,340 --> 00:18:21,340
 E tako je i ovo sve.

283
00:18:21,340 --> 00:18:22,580
 Kada imaš neko

284
00:18:22,580 --> 00:18:23,860
 ko te voli i motivira,

285
00:18:23,860 --> 00:18:25,740
 stvarno bez obzira na situaciju

286
00:18:25,740 --> 00:18:26,720
 kakvo smo mi bili,

287
00:18:26,720 --> 00:18:27,960
 vrijeme rata, svega,

288
00:18:27,960 --> 00:18:29,820
 ja njoj dižem spomenik.

289
00:18:29,820 --> 00:18:31,220
 Trebalo si ti moći odgojiti

290
00:18:31,220 --> 00:18:32,100
 petero djece.

291
00:18:32,100 --> 00:18:34,200
 Ona je petero djece odgajala

292
00:18:34,200 --> 00:18:35,180
 dok je on ratovo.

293
00:18:35,180 --> 00:18:37,440
 Ja ne dajem zasluge

294
00:18:37,440 --> 00:18:38,620
 ni jednom ni drugom.

295
00:18:38,620 --> 00:18:40,100
 Ko je sad više mene odgojio,

296
00:18:40,100 --> 00:18:42,120
 hajti rođo, ratuj,

297
00:18:42,120 --> 00:18:43,460
 a ona neko odgoja.

298
00:18:43,460 --> 00:18:44,160
 Pa rađe ti,

299
00:18:44,160 --> 00:18:46,060
 rađe bih ja i tebi pištaj,

300
00:18:46,060 --> 00:18:47,100
 pa ja ću biti sa djecom.

301
00:18:47,100 --> 00:18:48,220
 Znaš, to je isto tako,

302
00:18:48,220 --> 00:18:49,660
 kad se sjetim tih situacija

303
00:18:49,660 --> 00:18:50,240
 s tvojeg djetinstva,

304
00:18:50,240 --> 00:18:51,540
 ja sam isto ko ti iz Osijeka.

305
00:18:51,540 --> 00:18:54,900
 Odakle si?

306
00:18:54,900 --> 00:18:56,140
 Nas, Višnjivac.

307
00:18:56,140 --> 00:18:57,120
 Da, to lijepo.

308
00:18:57,120 --> 00:19:00,620
 I nas dvojice si mislimo

309
00:19:00,620 --> 00:19:01,640
 da smo imali neke teške

310
00:19:01,640 --> 00:19:02,720
 trenutke u životu.

311
00:19:02,720 --> 00:19:04,000
 Znaš, kad ti uspoređuješ

312
00:19:04,000 --> 00:19:05,740
 svoje djetinstvo

313
00:19:05,740 --> 00:19:06,760
 i kad se sjećaš sad,

314
00:19:06,760 --> 00:19:07,720
 u zreloj dobi

315
00:19:07,720 --> 00:19:08,860
 kad se sjetiš svoje majke,

316
00:19:08,860 --> 00:19:10,200
 kad malo provrtiš film,

317
00:19:10,200 --> 00:19:11,800
 sada kao zrela osoba

318
00:19:11,800 --> 00:19:12,360
 kad skužiš,

319
00:19:12,360 --> 00:19:13,180
 šta je ona prolazila?

320
00:19:13,180 --> 00:19:14,920
 Šta je tvoj otac prolazio?

321
00:19:14,920 --> 00:19:15,880
 Koje su to bile scene?

322
00:19:16,620 --> 00:19:17,680
 Dobro pa ja te kajem,

323
00:19:17,680 --> 00:19:18,480
 stvarno dobro,

324
00:19:18,480 --> 00:19:19,300
 vi su luđaci.

325
00:19:19,300 --> 00:19:20,060
 Ne,

326
00:19:20,060 --> 00:19:22,700
 znači ja sad kad se vratim nazad,

327
00:19:22,700 --> 00:19:23,920
 znači ja imam dvoje male djece,

328
00:19:23,920 --> 00:19:25,580
 curica 22 mjeseca,

329
00:19:25,580 --> 00:19:27,060
 sin 4 mjeseca.

330
00:19:27,060 --> 00:19:29,620
 I sad kad bi se ja zamislio

331
00:19:29,620 --> 00:19:31,260
 da živim u ratnom stanju,

332
00:19:31,300 --> 00:19:32,400
 uzeti pošku i ti...

333
00:19:32,400 --> 00:19:33,700
 I da mi je žena kod kuće

334
00:19:33,700 --> 00:19:35,320
 sa dvoje male djece.

335
00:19:35,320 --> 00:19:37,200
 I onda se staviš sve ono

336
00:19:37,200 --> 00:19:38,460
 što je dolazilo poslje rata,

337
00:19:38,460 --> 00:19:39,840
 i poslovni problemi,

338
00:19:39,840 --> 00:19:40,860
 i svakake pizdarije,

339
00:19:40,860 --> 00:19:41,820
 i smrti,

340
00:19:41,820 --> 00:19:42,620
 i svega i svega čega.

341
00:19:42,620 --> 00:19:44,360
 Ja skidam kapu svojim roditeljima,

342
00:19:44,360 --> 00:19:44,760
 ja ne znam.

343
00:19:44,760 --> 00:19:46,320
 Ja ne znam kako su oni živi,

344
00:19:46,320 --> 00:19:47,360
 zdravi i normalni uopće.

345
00:19:47,360 --> 00:19:49,800
 Slavonija je dala svoj doprnost,

346
00:19:49,800 --> 00:19:52,560
 upravo zbog toga mene jedan dan čovjek pito,

347
00:19:52,560 --> 00:19:53,860
 pa znaš ono,

348
00:19:53,860 --> 00:19:54,860
 ja sam čuo tebe,

349
00:19:54,860 --> 00:19:57,400
 ti si to tamo kao nešto glumio,

350
00:19:57,400 --> 00:19:59,200
 nekog skinhead-sa ovom...

351
00:19:59,200 --> 00:20:00,000
 Nisam te bro,

352
00:20:00,000 --> 00:20:00,860
 ja glumio ništa.

353
00:20:00,860 --> 00:20:02,240
 To tako bilo.

354
00:20:02,240 --> 00:20:04,260
 Tako se ljudi oblačili.

355
00:20:04,260 --> 00:20:06,880
 To se tamo tako u to vrijeme promoviralo.

356
00:20:06,880 --> 00:20:08,400
 Šta si ti 90-te,

357
00:20:08,400 --> 00:20:09,800
 evo gledaj sada reciziu,

358
00:20:09,800 --> 00:20:11,440
 di je to je Cajkaroški klubio?

359
00:20:11,440 --> 00:20:11,780
 Di?

360
00:20:11,780 --> 00:20:13,660
 Šta si mogo slušat?

361
00:20:13,660 --> 00:20:14,560
 Svi god tuđaš,

362
00:20:14,640 --> 00:20:16,460
 koji bjerti u njih dvojica, trojica priče,

363
00:20:16,460 --> 00:20:18,140
 joj, sjeća se kad sam ja...

364
00:20:18,140 --> 00:20:19,080
 Non-stop evo dan.

365
00:20:19,080 --> 00:20:20,240
 Danas ja znam došli tamo,

366
00:20:20,240 --> 00:20:21,720
 ista priča, razumiješ me?

367
00:20:21,720 --> 00:20:23,640
 Samo ti moraš,

368
00:20:23,640 --> 00:20:24,700
 ja kad sam došao u Zagreb,

369
00:20:24,700 --> 00:20:27,940
 ja sam se morao preformulirati totalno,

370
00:20:27,940 --> 00:20:28,940
 preobraziti.

371
00:20:28,940 --> 00:20:30,640
 Pa ovo nije to sada jedina,

372
00:20:30,640 --> 00:20:31,680
 frende, tu vidi ovo,

373
00:20:31,680 --> 00:20:33,640
 normalno vidi gej, vidi to.

374
00:20:33,640 --> 00:20:34,820
 Šta ti je, boraz?

375
00:20:34,820 --> 00:20:36,140
 To tamo nije normalno.

376
00:20:36,140 --> 00:20:37,300
 Znaš, ja sad ne znam,

377
00:20:37,300 --> 00:20:39,260
 ja 17 godina ne živim u Osijeku.

378
00:20:39,260 --> 00:20:40,980
 Ja ne znam kako je sad tamo.

379
00:20:40,980 --> 00:20:42,220
 Ali u moje vrijeme,

380
00:20:42,220 --> 00:20:43,580
 da se to dešavalo,

381
00:20:43,580 --> 00:20:44,340
 pa kaj ti rođe,

382
00:20:44,340 --> 00:20:45,600
 ti ne moš prođi kod skvartu.

383
00:20:45,600 --> 00:20:47,100
 Ili ti naselje.

384
00:20:47,100 --> 00:20:48,620
 Pa evo reci da li griješim.

385
00:20:48,620 --> 00:20:49,900
 Ja garantiram.

386
00:20:49,900 --> 00:20:51,640
 Mislim, to je tako bilo.

387
00:20:51,640 --> 00:20:53,780
 Znači, ja neću nikad zaboraviti scenu.

388
00:20:55,260 --> 00:20:56,740
 Znalazimo u naselje,

389
00:20:56,740 --> 00:20:58,200
 ko se njih dvojica,

390
00:20:58,200 --> 00:21:00,140
 krkana starih se čekaju,

391
00:21:00,140 --> 00:21:01,460
 oj, dođi dole,

392
00:21:01,460 --> 00:21:02,560
 spusti se dole.

393
00:21:02,560 --> 00:21:03,560
 Oje, šta se?

394
00:21:03,560 --> 00:21:05,980
 On je pušio na balkonu

395
00:21:05,980 --> 00:21:07,660
 i kak je pušio pamu, čiku,

396
00:21:07,660 --> 00:21:08,580
 njegovu kremu.

397
00:21:08,580 --> 00:21:09,560
 I on ga zove,

398
00:21:09,560 --> 00:21:11,020
 i sad djeca se okupila,

399
00:21:11,020 --> 00:21:11,280
 znaš,

400
00:21:11,280 --> 00:21:12,060
 i on ga zove,

401
00:21:12,060 --> 00:21:12,820
 siđi dole,

402
00:21:12,820 --> 00:21:13,720
 on se zagrijava.

